11UVW_INLINE TCPHandle::TCPHandle(ConstructorAccess ca, std::shared_ptr<Loop> ref, unsigned int f)
12 : StreamHandle{ca, std::move(ref)}, tag{f ? FLAGS : DEFAULT}, flags{f}
13{}
14
15
16UVW_INLINE bool TCPHandle::init() {
17 return (tag == FLAGS) ? initialize(&uv_tcp_init_ex, flags) : initialize(&uv_tcp_init);
18}
19
20
21UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::open(OSSocketHandle socket) {
22 invoke(&uv_tcp_open, get(), socket);
23}
24
25
26UVW_INLINE bool TCPHandle::noDelay(bool value) {
27 return (0 == uv_tcp_nodelay(get(), value));
28}
29
30
31UVW_INLINE bool TCPHandle::keepAlive(bool enable, TCPHandle::Time time) {
32 return (0 == uv_tcp_keepalive(get(), enable, time.count()));
33}
34
35
36UVW_INLINE bool TCPHandle::simultaneousAccepts(bool enable) {
37 return (0 == uv_tcp_simultaneous_accepts(get(), enable));
38}

41UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::bind(const sockaddr &addr, Flags<Bind> opts) {
42 invoke(&uv_tcp_bind, get(), &addr, opts);
43}

46template<typename I>
47UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::bind(std::string ip, unsigned int port, Flags<Bind> opts)
48{
49 typename details::IpTraits<I>::Type addr;
50 details::IpTraits<I>::addrFunc(ip.data(), port, &addr);
51 bind(reinterpret_cast<const sockaddr &>(addr), std::move(opts));
52}
53
54
55template<typename I>
56UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::bind(Addr addr, Flags<Bind> opts) {
57 bind<I>(std::move(addr.ip), addr.port, std::move(opts));
58}

61template<typename I>
62UVW_INLINE Addr TCPHandle::sock() const noexcept {
63 return details::address<I>(&uv_tcp_getsockname, get());
64}
65
66
67template<typename I>
68UVW_INLINE Addr TCPHandle::peer() const noexcept {
69 return details::address<I>(&uv_tcp_getpeername, get());
70}

73template<typename I>
74UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::connect(std::string ip, unsigned int port) {
75 typename details::IpTraits<I>::Type addr;
76 details::IpTraits<I>::addrFunc(ip.data(), port, &addr);
77 connect(reinterpret_cast<const sockaddr &>(addr));
78}
79
80
81template<typename I>
82UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::connect(Addr addr) {
83 connect<I>(std::move(addr.ip), addr.port);
84}
85
86
87UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::connect(const sockaddr &addr) {
88 auto listener = [ptr = shared_from_this()](const auto &event, const auto &) {
89 ptr->publish(event);
90 };
91
92 auto req = loop().resource<details::ConnectReq>();
93 req->once<ErrorEvent>(listener);
94 req->once<ConnectEvent>(listener);
95 req->connect(&uv_tcp_connect, get(), &addr);
96}
97
98
99UVW_INLINE void TCPHandle::closeReset() {
100 invoke(&uv_tcp_close_reset, get(), &this->closeCallback);
101}
